Project Title: Dijkstra-C  
Author: maximetinu  
Repository: https://github.com/Maximetinu/Dijkstra-C  
Language: C  
License: MIT

Overview:  
An open-source implementation of Dijkstra’s shortest path algorithm.  
Graph input via CSV or terminal. Visualization supported via Graphviz.

File Structure:  
- src/                     → Source code files  
- dijkstra.h              → Core algorithm declarations  
- IO_dijkstra.h           → Input/output utilities  
- graph_drawer.h          → Graphviz-based visualization interface  
- example_io_files/       → Sample CSV input/output files  

Function Summary:

1. calculate_shortest_path(...)  
   Location: dijkstra.h  
   Description: Computes shortest path using Dijkstra’s algorithm  
   Inputs: adjacency matrix, source node, target node  
   Outputs: shortest path and cost

2. read_graph_from_csv(...)  
   Location: IO_dijkstra.h  
   Description: Reads graph data from CSV file  
   Input: CSV file path  
   Output: adjacency matrix

3. print_path(...)  
   Location: IO_dijkstra.h  
   Description: Displays path in terminal  
   Input: path array, total distance  

4. write_output(...)  
   Location: IO_dijkstra.h  
   Description: Writes path and distance to file  
   Inputs: path array, distance, output path  

5. draw_graph(...)  
   Location: graph_drawer.h  
   Description: Visualizes graph and path using Graphviz  
   Inputs: graph data, path information  
   Output: DOT file or rendered image

